<h2><center>WORLD CLASS SOLUTIONS</H2></center>
<h3>HEI Incorporated</h3>

<p>
HEI is a Minnesota-based company specializing in the design and manufacture of ultraminiature microelectronic devices and high technology products incorporating those devices.  Most of HEI's products are custom devices, with HEI designing and producing unique microelectronic implementations to meet the state-of-the-art size, reliability or performance requirements of other manufacturers for their use in medical, computer peripheral, telecommunication and industrial control products.
<p>
The Company currently operates two domestic US facilities, both in Minnesota.  A headquarters plant in the Minneapolis suburb of Victoria is the primary fabrication facility for HEI's microcircuitry devices.  It also houses the Company's sales, design, engineering, quality, and corporate staff functions.
<p>

HEI's value-added assembly facility in Sauk Centre, Minnesota produces optoelectronic devices.
<P>
HEI takes pride in it's demonstrated leadership in meeting new and challenging circuit packaging requirements, and in the continuing improvement of these capabilities as evidenced by the Company's certification to the ISO 9001 International Quality Systems Standard, and a 25 year record of customer satisfaction. HEI has been publicly owned since 1981, with stock currently trading on the NASDAQ National Market under the symbol <font size=3><b>HEII</b></font size=3>

